   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "source": [
    "### 字典(dict)\n",
    "无序（Python 3.7+ 有序）、可变的键值对集合，键（key）必须是不可变类型（字符串、数字、元组），值（value）可以是任意类型，用 {} 表示。"
   ],
   "id": "996ed45a3825d7a1"
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-02-26T08:15:31.299970Z",
     "start_time": "2026-02-26T08:15:31.294879Z"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "dict1 = {}\n",
    "dict1['first'] = 123\n",
    "dict1['second'] = 456\n",
    "dict1"
   ],
   "id": "2e45db526907c340",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "{'first': 123, 'second': 456}"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 2,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "execution_count": 2
  },
  {
   "metadata": {
    "ExecuteTime": {
     "end_time": "2026-02-26T08:15:47.569306Z",
     "start_time": "2026-02-26T08:15:47.563919Z"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "code",
   "source": [
    "# 更新字典\n",
    "dict1['second'] = 789\n",
    "dict1"
   ],
   "id": "cc0c09d3eaafccc0",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "{'first': 123, 'second': 789}"
